This service is for those who provide a boutique feel for their guest. These host will enjoy extra services such as customized staging and restocking with priority scheduling.

POST STAY
Instant notification when the cleaner is on their way, starts and finishes the job.
Make sure the guests left the property in the condition in which they found it. 
Report any new visible damages in the property and take pictures 
INSPECTION
All lights turn on
All faucets work, and toilets flush
Kitchen major appliances work
Thermostat adjusted to preferred settings
Check Wi-Fi is up and running and all tvs turn on.
AUTOMATED SCHEDULING 
Automate cleaning bookings by syncing with our company calendar, and our system automatically assigns a cleaner to take care of your property on the day of check-out.

OTHER LIVING SPACES:

All surfaces dusted (including cobwebs, ceiling fans, picture frames, lamps, etc.)
Light organizing
Customize staging 
Wipe touch points (light switch, doors and doorknobs and remote controls)
Spot wipe minor smudges on walls if moisture tolerant 
Clean mirrors and glass tables
Cushions and pillows fluffed and straightened
Dust baseboards
Vacuum and wash all floors
Empty and clean all wastebaskets and replace liner from host supplies 






KITCHEN:
All surfaces dusted
Light organizing and restock dish soap and sponge if needed
Restock  and top up all kitchen cleaning supplies from the host supply cabinet
Dishes loaded in the dishwasher ( and taken out and put away in cupboards).
Remove perishables from the fridge and wipe shelves
Clean appliances exterior facings (stovetop, oven, fridge, microwave inside and out, dishwasher) 
Clean inside Oven only if deep clean has recently been 
Wipe cabinet facings
Wipe small appliances toaster, coffee maker, hot water kettle, blender etc.
Wipe table and chairs
Wipe and sanitize countertops
Empty and clean all wastebaskets and replace liner from host supplies 





BATHROOMS:
All surfaces dusted
Light organizing
Restocking Hand Soap and Toilet Paper 
Restock and top up all Bathroom supplies from the host supply cabinet
Wipe cabinet facings
Clean mirrors
Clean and sanitize showers, bathtubs and toilets and sinks 
Place fresh towels on the towel rack and a roll of toilet paper (from host stock)


BEDROOMS
All surfaces dusted
Light organizing
Make beds and change linens
Wipe mirrors and glass fixtures


LAUNDRY
We wash one load of linen and towels and transfer them into a dryer. Laundry is left in the dryer. We do not wait for the dryer cycle to complete to make the beds/ fold or hang towels. Extra linen and towel should be stocked in a secure locked cabinet. This will keep your cleaner within the time allotted for The Urban Cleaner Super Host package.
The Urban Cleaner Super Host Package
We wash, dry and fold linen and towels. We will put a load of laundry into a washer, transfer it into a dryer, take it out of the dryer and fold it. 
One load of laundry will be fully completed. Also, a second load will be left in the dryer if needed.
The Urban Cleaner Host Plus Package
We wash, dry and fold linen and towels. We will put a load of laundry into a washer, transfer it into a dryer, take it out of the dryer and fold it, place it neatly in designated storage space.
All of the laundries will be fully completed.
